<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Rosscarrock</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Provincially, Rosscarrock is in the Calgary-Currie and represented Christine Cusanelli and in the Calgary Centre federal riding, with no representation after the resignation of Lee Richardson.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Rosscarrock is located in Ward 6 and represented by Joe Connelly on the Calgary City Council. </p>
   <p class="par-lg">The CBE operates a public elementary school, with a Catholic, late French immersion school also in the area.</p>
        <p class="par-lg">Several medical clinics are located in the Westbrook Mall, from dentists to family doctors, as well as a chiropractic office and radiology consultants</p>
